function.name: str_replace_editor

extras.diff:
--- /workspace/solution.py
+++ /workspace/solution.py
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+import sys
@@ -1,0 +3,16 @@
+def main():
+    data = sys.stdin.read().strip().split()
+    if not data:
+        return
+    n = int(data[0])
+    a = list(map(int, data[1:1+n]))
+    # Check strictly increasing
+    for i in range(n-1):
+        if a[i] >= a[i+1]:
+            print("No")
+            return
+    print("Yes")
+
+if __name__ == "__main__":
+    main()
+
